      <p>In our testing, these gummies consistently produced noticeable drowsiness within 20-30 minutes. The blackberry flavor is genuinely pleasant without being overly sweet, and the texture is soft without being sticky. At $0.23 per serving, they undercut most competitors that offer a comparable ingredient profile.</p>

