      <p>If your primary goal is straightforward melatonin supplementation at the lowest possible cost, Natrol is difficult to beat. At $0.10 per serving with 90 servings per bottle, you are looking at a full three-month supply for under $10. Natrol is the number-one selling melatonin brand in America, and their gummies maintain the same quality standards that built that reputation.</p>

